                <note rend="inline" type="source">882.51/1499a: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to the
                        Minister in Liberia</hi> (<persName type="to">
                        <hi rend="italic">Hood</hi>
                    </persName>)</head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1922-06-05T15:00:00-04:00">
                            <hi rend="italic">June 5, 1922—3 p.m.</hi>
                        </date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>18. Joint Resolution to authorize $5,000,000 loan to Liberia reported favorably
                    to Senate May 31st by Senate Finance Committee. It is hoped Senate will take
                    prompt action on Resolution. Inform Liberian Government.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Hughes</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
